            <h3 class="headline white">The Challenge</h3>
            <p class="text white">
              Neuron brand already has several services by one brand, it has focused on another one.
              We were tasked with design the modern and delightful iOS app for mobility sharing system so that the visual
              style will be consistent with the general brand and will open new opportunities for Neuron’s system users.
            </p>
            <div class="pg-section">
              <h3 class="headline white">The Problem</h3>
              <p class="text white">
                The goal was to create a functional and complex app with delightful experience and
                allow users to be happy to share rides with friends and have rides for points.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
